We have JIRA customized with the following issue types (Requirement, Feature, Enhancement, Use Case, Test Case, Defect, Task). When I link to other issues...I need to be able to identify what the issue type is. Currently, we are using a mnemonic (e.g. RQ) to identify the issue type for linking but this is extra typing for something that is already captured by JIRA.

